FBIS4-60191 "drnes099_j_94019" FBIS-NES-94-099 Daily Report 20 May 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Wrapup of Reports on Clashes, Military Operations Wrapup of Reports on Clashes, Military Operations North To Observe 3-Day Cease-Fire NC2005203294 Paris AFP in English 2029 GMT 20 May 94 NC2005203294 Paris AFP English BFN [Text] Sanaa, May 20 (AFP)--The Yemen Government will observe a three-day cease-fire following 15 days of fighting with southern forces, the northern-controlled SABA' news agency reported Friday. The ceasefire, effective from Saturday 0:00 a.m. (Friday 2100 GMT), was declared on the occasion of the Muslim 'Id al-Adha festival prior to Sunday's celebration of the fourth anniversary of the unification of South and North Yemen, the agency said.
